The Senior Special Assistant to President Muhammadu Buhari on Media and Publicity, Garba Shehu, has on Friday apologised for incorrectly stating that only ten boys were kidnapped at the Government Science School in Kankara, Katsina State. Gunmen, who came on motorbikes, had last Friday invaded the school's premises around 11 pm, shooting indiscriminately to scare away the residents.  See Also






